 # Secrets Management Runbook

## Overview

All passwords, credentials, and secrets are managed using a two-tier approach: 1. Vaultwarden for human password storage and retrieval 2. Ansible Vault for infrastructure automation secrets

This eliminates hardcoded credentials and provides centralized secrets management with encryption at rest.

